# Paradigms

FP preferred: pure fns, immutability, map/filter/reduce.
state: derive > store. compute from source of truth. no duplicated state.
local-first: SQLite via sqlite-wasm + OPFS. no network = no problem.
  schema versioning: user_version PRAGMA. check at boot, run migrations if stale.
  migrations: additive only (add columns/tables). never drop/rename without version bump.
  queries: raw SQL in lib/db/queries/. no ORM. typed return shapes in types/.
  ephemeral UI state (theme, open panels): localStorage only. never in SQL